NAME
    Dist::Zilla::Plugin::PodWeaverIfPod - Apply PodWeaver if there is
    already Pod

SYNOPSIS
    In your Dist::Zilla `dist.ini':

        [PodWeaverIfPod]

DESCRIPTION
    Dist::Zilla::Plugin::PodWeaverIfPod will only PodWeaver a .pm if there
    appears to be Pod there (i.e. a `=head1' section).

